Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:12.51,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:18.00,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget what I was like before I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:22.41,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind caresses my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:24.74,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,♪Lullaby of Birdland♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.74,0:00:29.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick my heels going down the slope
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:32.73,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,As my worthless shadow grows　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:37.84,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an endless summer vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.84,0:00:43.54,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like sneakin' into the swimming pool
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:49.60,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's swim with our clothes on, jump in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:52.27,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A shocking seductive spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.27,0:00:56.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This beat that pierces my heart is strange　
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:00.18,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(It flares up, then vanishes)　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:02.37,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Every miserable day is swell,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:03.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,dress it up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:06.90,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A high-speed swing surrounds us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.88,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(What's this dance called? I can't stop)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:14.96,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you go, it's twined around my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:20.14,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,and won't leave me ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.42,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:28.90,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,...is like love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:41.19,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:42.76,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:46.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Can I really keep these?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:49.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably some mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.69,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mukae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:57.93,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.39,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Cold today, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:01.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:03.78,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:04.77,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:09.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Can't let \Nmyself get my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've already been rejected once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.60,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the usual, Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.43,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:26.46,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! You're looking \Nbeautiful as always, Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.58,0:02:32.21,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you. What's with the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:37.88,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a guess. You're in shock over \Nthe news that Yurika-senpai eloped?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.43,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:44.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did you tell him about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:47.89,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kawabuchi-kun? Yeah, \NI told him this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.76,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's in the classroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:54.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to hear anything like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:57.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How must he feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:15.38,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's the one that won the \NPrefectural Governor's Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:17.53,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better take it down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:19.17,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,You take that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:21.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:24.23,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way the school \Nwill display a painting
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.07,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,by a student who's involved in a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:28.07,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,We were told to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:30.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And what's going to happen \Nto it after you take it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.69,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,You got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:35.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! This painting is important!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:36.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.63,0:03:40.36,Main Dialog,Boy B,0000,0000,0000,,What's she to you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.11,Main Dialog,Boy A,0000,0000,0000,,Had eyes for her, did ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.05,0:03:45.66,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:51.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. You can take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:53.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen! Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care what happens \Nto that painting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:04.97,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing?! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Your stupidity must be contagious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:16.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, how stupid are you \Ngonna be for somebody else's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:20.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. What about the painting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:23.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I already said my \Ngoodbye to it back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.33,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.28,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten a present \Nfrom someone recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:41.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Like something that was knitted...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.38,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:49.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I knitted Sentaro a sweater and used \Nthe leftover yarn to make the mittens!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:52.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel... But it figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:57.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This! It's called Lily-yarn or something. \NI got it from Sachiko yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:04:59.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.61,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.18,0:05:06.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But what am I supposed \Nto do with this string?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you...?! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.95,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.43,0:05:26.41,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:35.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, these are really warm... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Dammit! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we'll be \Nchanging classes again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess third-years are split up \Naccording to their grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:00.31,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,so you probably won't be in \Nthe same class as Kaoru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Goin' for college entrance \Nexams, right Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to go to college, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:12.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about becoming \Nan elementary school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna be a teacher, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.68,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:21.65,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Long time ago, you said you wanted \Nto have a bakery or cake shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.12,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What? When was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:27.64,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't you remember? \NYou were a glutton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:29.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you wanted a shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.13,0:06:35.04,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, where do you \Nwant to go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:40.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I... haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:46.86,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,As for me, never mind about college. I \Nmight not even make it to third-year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:51.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it all comes down \Nto the next make-up exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Start with these basic problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you some flash \Ncards in the meanwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not cut out for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.20,0:07:10.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do if you fail this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll just quit school an' get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about my family, I \Ncan't afford to repeat a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:23.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you flunk this test!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.39,0:07:51.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired. I need a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You're in the middle \Nof these questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.20,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to rest, it'll have to \Nwait 'til you're done with these problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:01.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! My head's gonna explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.48,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:15.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:20.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You look really happy when \Nyou're surrounded by children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where'd that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.36,0:08:26.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're going to have \Na big family of your own,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,with lots of kids around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:30.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.48,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Chi'ko wet herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.83,0:08:37.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wet herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:38.96,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, Chi'ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:48.73,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The bath's over there. My ma will dry \Nyour pants, so relax in the meantime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is an unusual setup for a bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of soap, right? Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:14.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:19.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't understand. Isn't \Nthis Sen's family's bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:23.39,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,We share the bath with Sentaro's family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:33.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I wish I had given the \Nmittens to you earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:38.11,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost spring, so you won't \Nneed to use them anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that doesn't matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:47.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since you knitted the mittens, Ri-chan, \NI'd like to wear them all year 'round.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:49.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:52.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Condensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:58.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Drops often fall in there. Sentaro lets \Nout a yelp once in a while himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:04.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ri-chan, why did you \Ngive me those mittens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.23,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.92,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why me and not him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:21.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... if you've liked \Nhim all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.03,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie! How about havin' dinner here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:37.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Your pants aren't dry yet anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:39.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.13,0:10:41.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.87,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, your hair's soakin' \Nwet! You'll catch cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:03.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to say that to Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:08.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't get it out of my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:13.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That she probably still \Nhas feelings for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.87,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Sen, how did the make-up exam go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.16,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:30.75,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.31,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to Richie. I \Ngotta thank 'im proper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:38.44,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I haven't \Nseen Richie-rich lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:41.42,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,The day before yesterday, he \Npassed out in class with a fever,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,so he's restin' up at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.41,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:47.44,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, Ritsuko didn't say a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:14.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,"Someday My Prince Will Come"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:18.55,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:21.72,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko. Would you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:29.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it. Huge, ain't \Nit? That's Richie's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:35.37,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank Richie for me, for helpin' me study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:36.42,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.48,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:39.26,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Go on by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:42.64,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Let's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:49.36,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, one of your classmates \Nhas come to wish you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.37,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:01.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is your fever down?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:04.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Sorry to make you worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.95,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:10.44,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. These are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.98,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Eat them if you're up to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:16.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you. Did you go \Nout of the way to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:22.49,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... No. I didn't buy these. Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:23.89,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:30.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan. He came here with you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:33.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you two out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:35.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He should've come in with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.32,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.81,0:13:41.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:48.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense. You two have been \Ntogether since you were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:51.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could be a match for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:57.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike me, he's strong... and built...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:01.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And so handsome, he even takes \Nmy breath away once in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:05.99,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, you're better off with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:13.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you're saying, \Nso don't say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:28.22,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, don't you like me anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:33.99,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,...you just don't have any confidence, \Nso you're trying to keep your distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:39.30,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, you told me to \Nhave confidence in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:44.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Those words have saved me a number of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But if it looks like you \Ndon't have confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:51.06,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling I'll lose mine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:15:00.29,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:05.76,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What I've wished for all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.16,0:15:09.07,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.18,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:18.39,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy! I bet something \Nhappened between those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:31.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come here... I'll go over to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:51.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan... Let me tell you how I \Nfeel about you one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:59.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:00.57,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:06.19,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! Your relatives can hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:17.62,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not muscular and maybe I'm \Nnot as manly as I should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:22.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but when it comes to my feelings for \Nyou, Ri-chan, I'm second to no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:29.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You might catch my cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.07,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I won't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.02,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:41.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're burning up! And you're heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.15,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,That was really something...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.79,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:01.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is summer already and I haven't \Nmade any more progress with Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was that \Nbold when I had a fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me when \Nmy temperature is normal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.27,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Touch what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:13.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:13.63,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.16,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.16,0:17:16.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.54,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.94,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,East High Newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,"The Olympus Has Thrown Down the Gauntlet"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.47,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:28.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,"The Olympus is going to win \Nat this year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru to Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there are still some \Nold-fashioned jazz musicians around,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.56,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,but this is the era of rock n' roll."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:37.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,They were handing this \Nout all over the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:41.56,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do? I mean, you \Ncan't take this sitting down, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:43.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You two are gonna perform in \Nthe festival, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:46.67,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.07,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.07,0:17:51.09,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:55.91,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We start with "Moanin'" to fire up \Nthe people that saw us last year
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:59.21,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,an' fake 'em out thinking we're \Ngonna do the same routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:02.56,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But then we move into some other \Nsongs that we want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:05.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinkin' the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:07.22,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's choose our next song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, we'd better \Npractice every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:10.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,'Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:12.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.85,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.28,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:19.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:19.96,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:21.70,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I got surprising news!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.43,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Dad says he's comin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.87,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,This way, the whole family can live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.08,0:18:36.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sa-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:39.93,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:49.61,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I'm actually scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:57.30,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,See, our Dad, who was working far \Naway, is coming home tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:02.62,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, I'm one of those that ain't \Ngot a place in the house, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.35,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Richie...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:11.97,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:14.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're back late, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's Richie doin' here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:25.29,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Unlike with Kota \Nand the other little ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:28.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,you remember how scary Dad \Nwas when he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.64,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry, Sachiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:37.11,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ma told me that Dad worked really \Nhard an' quit drinkin' over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:39.24,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You got nothin' \Nto worry about, Sachiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:46.06,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Now how about comin' inside \Nan' we can prepare together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:46.66,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.63,0:19:55.51,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks for lookin' after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:59.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I'm worried about, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:10.48,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Dope! What are you lookin' so serious for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I am serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.82,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie. Don't worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:18.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.43,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:23.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Comin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:23.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to practice tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:34.49,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. After all, playin' with \Nyou is the most fun I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.72,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, what are you writin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.36,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Nah, that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's not comin' out right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:55.58,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well. Let's get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:06.58,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie. I'm sorry for lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:11.52,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking forward to the \Nfestival, too. I wanted to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Be good to Ri'ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:16.59,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:28.64,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for you on that slope　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:36.92,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,For our after school promise　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.91,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a 'goodbye' blurred far away　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:56.22,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so weak, so awkward, and so fragile back then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:22:03.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,But you gave me a small pair of wings　         　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:09.83,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,In the twilight hour of the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:15.48,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for a gleam of light　　　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:23.45,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could have said that I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:35.72,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The note that I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:48.80,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,has never been delivered to this day
